  "name": "Morrison COU2 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 5, fully assessed)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels with sufficient fidelity to support regulatory submission for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed at high rigor with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel. Full uncertainty quantification, sensitivity analysis, and validation against independent experimental datasets are documented.",
